testcase.name: AppComponent should create the app
AppComponent should have as title 'ATT&CKÂ® Navigator'
ChangelogComponent should create
ConfigService should be created
ControlFrameworkImportComponent should create
ControlFramework initialization should be truthy

ControlFramework initialization should have cis items
ControlFramework initialization should have owasp items
ControlFramework initialization should have techniquesNist
ControlFramework initialization should have asvsNist80053Mapping
ControlFramework initialization should have mitigationNist

ControlFramework getCisItemsByNistSubCatId should get 1 CIS Items by nist sub cat is DE.CM-7

ControlFramework getNistItemByNistSubCatId should get a CIS Items by nist sub cat is DE.CM-7
ControlFramework getNistItemByNistSubCatId should get null for nist sub cat id "DOESNOTEXIST"
ControlFramework getTechniqueMapping should return null when given a null technique
ControlFramework getTechniqueMapping should return an enriched technique when given a valid technique
ControlFramework getNistItemsWithMappings should be truthy
ControlFramework getMitigations should be truthy
ATT&CK model objects should wire relationships and class helpers
DataService should be created
DataService should handle version setup correctly
DataService should get domain by identifier
DataService should handle STIX data parsing
DataService should identify valid technique-like objects through parse
DataService should filter deprecated and revoked objects
DataService should parse relationships and matrices/tactics
DataService should compute VersionChangelog differences
DataService getDomainData includes Basic auth header when configured
DataService getDomainData caches the created Observable when refresh=false
DataService loadDomainData resolves; invalid domain rejects
DataService loadDomainData when already loaded (no refresh) still triggers request in current implementation
DataService compareVersions branches: revocations, deprecations, changes vs minor
DataService utilities: getDomainVersionID and getCurrentVersion

HelpComponent should create

LayerInformationComponent should create
ChangelogCellComponent should create

MatrixFlatComponent should create

MatrixSideComponent should create
TacticCellComponent should create
ContextmenuComponent should create
TechniqueCellComponent can create an instance of TechniqueCellComponent
TechniqueCellComponent #onMouseEnter() and #onMouseLeave() emit with highlighted and un-highlighted techniques, respectively
TooltipComponent should create
AsvsTableComponent should create
CisTableComponent should create
NistMappingsComponent should create
MitigationsComponent should ...
SidebarComponent should create
TabsComponent (logic only) getUniqueLayerName increments correctly
TabsComponent (logic only) newBlankTab opens a new tab and selects it
TabsComponent (logic only) openTab selects existing tab when not forced
TabsComponent (logic only) openTab replace closes active and inserts new tab
TabsComponent (logic only) closeTab selects appropriate next tab or opens new blank when none
TabsComponent (logic only) indexToChar and charToIndex map only data tabs
TabsComponent (logic only) hasFeature proxies to config service and dialogs open
VersionUpgradeComponent should create
ViewModelsService controls and aggregation filterTechniques filters by platforms but not for PRE-ATT&CK
ViewModelsService controls and aggregation isSubtechniqueEnabled returns true when a subtechnique is enabled and matches platform
ViewModelsService controls and aggregation sortTechniques respects modes 0-3 and numeric tie-breakers
ViewModelsService controls and aggregation calculateAggregateScore covers average/min/max/sum and countUnscored toggle
Filter helpers initPlatformOptions, toggle, inFilter, serialize/deSerialize
Gradient utility should initialize with a default preset and serialize/deserialize
Gradient utility should change presets and update gradient
Gradient utility should map values to gradient endpoints
Gradient utility should add and remove colors
ViewModelsService inheritance in layer ops inherits fields, filters, legendItems, and gradient
ViewModel initialization and static score initTechniqueVMs populates techniqueVMs and static scoring sets binary gradient
ViewModelsService.layerLayerOperation combines scores across VMs and updates gradient
LayoutOptions enforces valid layouts and toggles showName/showID with mini
LayoutOptions serialize/deserialize roundtrip
ViewmodelsService should be created
TechniqueVM helpers annotated and modified reflect state and resetAnnotations clears
TechniqueVM helpers deSerialize sets fields from JSON
